```

## Theme CSS Variables

Use Tailwind's theme colors:

- `bg-background` - Main background
- `bg-card` - Card background
- `bg-primary` - Primary color
- `bg-secondary` - Secondary color
- `text-foreground` - Main text
- `text-muted-foreground` - Muted text
- `border` - Border color
